  - Matches arena/AOR character: tight 3–4‑minute riffs and singalong orientation match my 3–5‑minute riff‑driven preference.
  - Vocal stacks: “massive center‑front multitracked harmonies” and “dense vocal overdubs” align directly with my preference for huge stacked vocal harmonies and vocal‑forward clarity when supported by backing stacks.
  - Transients and headroom: explicit “tape‑like transient punch” and “preserved headroom” fit my desire for preserved transient guitar attack and generous headroom with restrained tape saturation.
