3) Why I choose Candidate 2 and reject Candidate 1
- Choice rationale: Candidate 2 aligns much more closely with the core of my stated preferences: arena/AOR framing (riff lengths and singalong orientation), massive multitracked harmonies up front, preserved transient punch and generous headroom, restrained low end and roomy imaging — all of which are explicitly called out in the description. Those attributes hit the primary buckets in my self‑introduction: midrange/tape‑tinge, vocal stacks, transient preservation, low compression and an arena sheen appropriate for riff‑driven singalongs.
